Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:10.66,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:18.88,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:37.51,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King gives stars\Nto the Magic Knights Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,for every achievement they accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:41.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The squads compete to obtain the most stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:45.31,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Star Festival is where the\N number of stars each squad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:50.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,has accumulated in that year \Nis announced to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:53.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,While the usually peaceful \NStar Festival was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:57.24,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami and the captain of the \NGreen Praying Mantises, Jack the Ripper,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:01.83,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,decide to battle it out \Nover something insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.70,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Abra and cadabra.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:10.50,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Their issues were resolved by \Nan unexpected turn of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:14.38,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone returned to the Star Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:44.04,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(187,1)}The Briar Maiden's Melancholy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.83,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:52.73,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's so elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.24,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is she from some wealthy family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:56.07,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, go talk to her, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:57.73,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No way! How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:01.98,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She is super pretty. I bet \NFinral would love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:07.53,main,Balmain,0000,0000,0000,,Truly exquisite. I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:10.66,Default,Balmain,0000,0000,0000,,You will be my companion tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's Baron Balmain from \Nthe House of Bamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.91,0:03:17.91,Default,Balmain,0000,0000,0000,,First, let us enjoy this festival together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.55,Default,Balmain,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:27.14,Default,Balmain,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring me, are you? You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:30.43,Default,Balmain,0000,0000,0000,,Just who do you think I am? I'mâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.23,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.02,Default,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.73,Default,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,That would be my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.82,top,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,We don't get to enjoy festivals \Nlike this every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:43.86,sign_5273_31_Blue_Rose_Knight,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(466,1)}Blue Rose Knights Squad, 3rd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Sol Marron
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.86,top,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,so let's doll ourselves up a bit, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.74,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:49.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.89,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's the captain of the Blue Rose Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.33,sign_5584_37_Blue_Rose_Knight,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(968,1)}Blue Rose Knights Captain\N{\fs30}Charlotte Roselei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.92,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doin', Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.64,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.80,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.67,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.51,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Were you planning to use \Nme as some accessory?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.31,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,And without my consent, no less.\NWhat were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:17.58,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,The House of Bamilton? I belong \Nto the House of Roselei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:22.81,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you could approach me \Nso casually because I'm a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:26.66,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a single way in \Nwhich you are superior to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... where did Asta run off to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:38.60,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he did take quite a flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:41.60,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I've ever seen so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.33,main,Kiato,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to take my hand at \Nany time so you don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:52.89,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Use your magic \Nto do something about my briars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:57.23,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! You go, Sis! You're as cool as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.05,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.32,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! \NYou're supposed to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's seriously gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:09.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong? Did you find Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.95,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like some drunk is \Ndancing naked over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.89,main,Kahono,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing for royalty to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.45,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:22.57,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The little runt from the \Ndistinguished service ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you callin' a runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:26.08,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're definitely a little runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you giant woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:30.10,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that, you little mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.56,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to stomp you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:36.27,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.97,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.37,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You got it, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.28,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I found this super awesome dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.45,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,What I have on right now is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.99,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll look great in it, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.24,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.24,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.51,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:55.00,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:58.98,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! Your skin is as \Nlovely and pale as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.77,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,It's smoother than marble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.50,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:12.30,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking at a festival is \Non a whole 'nother level!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:17.58,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Eating at a festival makes the \Nfood taste even more delicious, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:19.00,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,S-So many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.86,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed! Nom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.19,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow. It really is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.65,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to come with Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.34,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes special somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:31.17,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because we're at a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.66,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it must be because I'm \Nwith you, Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:42.37,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Festivals get me so pumped up! \NThe inner man in me is raring to get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.96,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? Wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.46,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:47.15,sign_9750_96_Festivals___,Gordon/cap,0000,0000,0000,,Festivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.70,sign_9750_96_Festivals___,Gordon/cap,0000,0000,0000,,By being able to enjoy a different environment\Nthan we ordinarily experience in our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.49,sign_9750_96_Festivals___,Gordon/cap,0000,0000,0000,,our bonds become even stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:53.74,sign_9750_96_Festivals___,Gordon/cap,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.64,sign_9750_96_Festivals___,Gordon/cap,0000,0000,0000,,An unforgettable page in\N our book of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:07:00.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm zero for five today. \NI'm doing worse than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Sniffity, sniffity, sniff-sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:04.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I smell an extremely beautiful lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.11,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What's his problem? There are plenty \Nof pretty girls right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.90,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:15.49,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, \Nwhat's taking the captain so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:25.21,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You look awesome, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.55,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,That helmet you always wear looks \Ngreat on you, but so does this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:32.55,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A goddess... I'm truly in the \Npresence of a goddess right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's super pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:42.27,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down, men. This isn't a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.44,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:48.97,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones allowed to get all excited \Nabout Sis's beauty are the Blue Rose Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.69,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:55.95,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I can't let the other \Ncaptains see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.20,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Especially not {\i0}him{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Seems pretty rowdy over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:03.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Y'all enjoying the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.67,sign_11611_120_Raging_Bull,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Bull
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.67,sign_11611_121_Festival,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:06.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid. You still in one piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:11.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on! I almost got hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:14.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Like that's enough to hurt {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:19.47,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.35,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Why in the world did he have to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.23,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a goddess, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.25,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,No... I cannot lose my \Ncomposure in front of Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.58,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down... Calm down, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:33.70,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait. He might not even \Nrecognize me in this dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Her Cold and Prickly Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.45,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Badump!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's with the sparkly outfit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.87,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe. Stay calm... Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.63,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you? What are those \Nstrange clothes you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:53.13,sign_12699_137_Festival,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:53.13,sign_12699_138_Raging_Bull,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Bull
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:53.13,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Especially your lower half! \NWhat in the world is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:58.10,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're the dirtiest, \Nmacho-est guy out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.85,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:05.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you aren't training your \Nsquad members properly, rose girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:09.61,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't you dare come any closer \Nto Sis dressed in that weird outfit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.11,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Sol, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:17.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Captain! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.45,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Come drink with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Hey, Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.16,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.97,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why... but I feel like \NI can't afford to lose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's the Captain of the Blue Rose Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.67,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,This woman... She's so incredibly \Nfriendly with Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.82,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a member of the Black Bulls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.89,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.94,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are, glaring at Sis \Nlike that? You're just a Black Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.62,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not glaring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:58.61,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,A Black Bull couldn't beat Sis \Nin a billion, trillion years!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A billion, trillion years, eh? Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.68,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let the Blue Rose Knights \Nkeep talking to us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:10.46,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't embarrass Captain Yami any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.23,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:14.67,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:21.61,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous. There's little time left before\N our achievements are announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.80,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Why would anyone bother toâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:26.01,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! There's no way Sis would lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:27.81,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're actually doing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.49,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of battle shall it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:47.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm more powerful \Nnow than I've ever been before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:50.37,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:53.71,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.13,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Captain of the Blue Rose Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:59.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is turning into a huge mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:01.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.73,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, now, my lovely ladies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.43,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We're at a festival, so why \Ndon't we all just get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.72,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man. Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.44,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:12.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You only know how to flirt \Nwith girls. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.65,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.44,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect for a festival night! \NA battle befitting two gorgeous ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A cosplay contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.33,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.54,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What? Scared of losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:33.71,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! There's nothing in this \Nworld that Sis can't look good in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.37,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Things seem rather lively over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.04,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we are at a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:48.44,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There doesn't seem to be any trouble,\N so I'm sure it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:51.94,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us head to where they will announce \Nthe achievements. We mustn't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.33,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:56.20,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,The announcement of our achievements...\N I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.54,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be nervous about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.53,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We will undoubtedly come out on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:06.37,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Right. But I think the Black Bulls \Nworked rather hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:11.68,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, they might have. \NActually, I know they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.91,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We must especially keep an eye \Non all of Asta's achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.30,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,B-But he's still just a Black Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:21.51,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They're full of problems, \Nregardless of their achievements!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.38,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,They are no match for us, the Golden Dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.41,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:30.70,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls are the lowest \Nof the low. Them, beat us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:31.89,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:38.64,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,First up, we have the Captain of the \NBlue Rose Knights, Charlotte Roselei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.73,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The cosplay she chose is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.30,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A sexy little witchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:46.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about super rare! Yee-haw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:51.87,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,We chose the same outfit as that one witch \Njust to show how much better Sis is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:55.58,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The difference is super clear! \NSexy little witchie Sis is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:13:00.64,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. There's no way \NI'd lose to that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.09,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Also, call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.84,sign_11611_120_Raging_Bull,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Raging Bull
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.06,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.93,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I wear something like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.81,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look! Don't look at me, Yami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:15.29,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, maybe there's a part \Nof me that wants you to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.94,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he'd be a little \Nfriendlier to me if I dressed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:21.09,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,like that girl who's way \Ntoo friendly with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.29,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too embarrassing! Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:24.86,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:28.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue Rose Knights' captain \Nlooks pretty good in that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:36.01,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, we have a member of the \NBlack Bulls, Vanessa Enoteca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.87,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The cosplay she chose is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.79,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,No one saw this coming! \NShe's dressed as a sister of the cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.88,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her slay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.63,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, you don't know \Nanything about guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.85,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like this sort of contrast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:54.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,She's usually exposing so much \Nthat this is actually sexy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:58.14,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,May God watch over you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Miz Vanessa is glowing more than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:11.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone! Send your magic \Npowers to the girl you like best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.66,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely voting for the \Nsexy little witchie, Charlotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.70,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The sister's good, too, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.75,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I don't know which to choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.00,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,And let's stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:24.37,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,As for the results...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! They received \Nthe same amount of points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:27.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.37,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:34.10,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. This doesn't matter anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:38.22,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,A draw? After I bothered to dress like this? \NI've shamed the House of Roselei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:39.06,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:43.27,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Y-Yami thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.07,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Does he see me in a different light now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.91,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Then my embarrassment might be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.63,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Sis got a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.53,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.83,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:00.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Round two will \Nbe a swimsuit competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.13,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you two, striâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:06.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I think I kinda like this... \NI mean... I-I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:10.84,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who agrees with him \Nwill endure the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:17.59,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Our Clover Premium Beer uses ingredients \Nfrom right here in the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:22.74,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's rich and smooth, but you can \Nstill taste some fruity undertones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.23,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Try a sip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.24,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain, you like a girl who \Ncan hold her liquor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.07,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Badump, badump...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:36.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:39.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can drink together. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.33,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.08,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.84,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have a drinking contest next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.30,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,This is nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.52,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I've entertained you this long,\N but that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:53.84,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to announce \Nour achievements soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.18,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to go, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:16:00.60,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring her down and show \Nthat insolent girl who's boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:06.97,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:10.58,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will be decided by who \Ncan drink the most booze in an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.58,0:16:13.79,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The beer we'll be drinking is \Nthis special Clover Premium.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:14.99,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Clover Kingdom's best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.21,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,No chugging allowed, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.89,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have any little ones copying us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.87,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,and we need to savor the flavor \Nout of respect to the brewers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.12,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.88,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let the games begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.69,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You got this, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:33.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on, \Nbut you can do it, Miz Vanessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.14,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that this woman \Nis a pretty heavy drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.18,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a difficult match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:45.73,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.60,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.29,italicstop,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she already \Ndrank herself under the table!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:49.19,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not drunk at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.77,italicstop,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she proposed \Nthis battle in that condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:53.61,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.11,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I can win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.38,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! She can't hold her liquor at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.62,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,But that's another thing \Nthat's so cute about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:11.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are those two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:16.65,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my cool because this was over Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:19.51,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.70,flashbackitalics,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,A curse... I place a curse \Nupon the House of Roselei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:31.56,flashback,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,When your daughter turns eighteen, \Nthe curse will activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:36.24,flashback,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It will engulf you all and trap \Nyou within a cage of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:42.06,flashback,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how can this be, Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:45.21,flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could figure out \Nhow to break the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:49.07,flashback,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't cry, Mother and Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:52.39,flashback,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become stronger. Stronger than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.71,flashback,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,And I will overcome this curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:58.31,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she raised her rank again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:02.42,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That newbie from the \NBlue Rose Knights is so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.23,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.62,flashback,Suitor,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Charlotte, please marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:13.13,flashback,Suitor 2,0000,0000,0000,,No, marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:20.12,flashback,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot defeat me, \Nyou could never accept my curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:27.62,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surrounded by weak men who are all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:32.42,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I will overcome this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.41,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:39.17,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The curse upon the House \Nof Roselei has activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.18,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use. We can't stop it! Ruâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.86,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,It won't... stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:55.15,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:19:00.66,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Curses! How pathetic... I'm so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:09.66,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry... Mother and Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:28.22,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's the big idea, you jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:32.15,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You flung the pasta soup \NI was eating everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:38.01,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Yami Sukehiro? To think I'd let him see \Nme in such a disgraceful situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.15,flashbackitalics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,What a failure I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:46.23,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,On missions, you're as cool as a cucumber \Nand always raring to go. So what gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.66,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I like tough girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:56.17,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But it probably wouldn't hurt to ask\Nsomeone for help once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:05.39,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Our Magic Knights Squads are full \Nof strong people you can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.51,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,To have my heart stolen by a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:14.48,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,That was the way to break the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.36,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sweet. It's disappearing. Lucky for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:24.67,italics,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a barbarian. \NHe's so aggravating, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:32.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can't finish it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:35.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you not to push \Nyourself too much before?
